Proposed law provides for the general re-creation of the DOTD and its statutory entities,
effective June 30, 2026, in accordance with "sunset" law.
Proposed law supersedes the provisions of the "sunset" law which set out the procedure for
review and re-creation and requires a separate bill to re-create each statutory entity within
the department along with additional provisions.
Proposed law makes July 1, 2031 the new termination date and provides that termination
begins July 1, 2030, unless the department is re-created again.
Effective June 30, 2026.
(Adds R.S. 49:191(3)(b); Repeals R.S. 49:191(1)(o))
